appointmentslots

Class AppointmentSlotManagementControl

  • java.lang.Object
    • appointmentslots.AppointmentSlotManagementControl

  • public class AppointmentSlotManagementControl
extends java.lang.Object
    Manages the appointment slots for doctors, allowing operations such as viewing available slots, viewing personal schedules, and setting doctor availability.

      • viewAppointmentSlots

        public void viewAppointmentSlots()
        Views all appointment slots for a given doctor based on their doctor ID. Prompts the user to enter a doctor ID and displays all the available slots.

      • viewAvailableTimeSlots

        public void viewAvailableTimeSlots()
        Views available time slots for a doctor within the next 14 days. Prompts the user to select a doctor and date to view available time slots.
